THESE TERMS AND CONDITIONS SHALL APPLY TO AND REGULATE THE WINGCOIN PROGRAM MADE AVAILABLE OR ISSUED BY WINGINTER TO YOU. IT IS IMPORTANT THAT YOU READ CAREFULLY AND UNDERSTAND THE FOLLOWING TERMS AND CONDITIONS BEFORE USAGE OF THE WINGCOIN PROGRAM.

1.	DEFINITIONS
Wingcoin Program refers to loyalty program initiated by WingInter, by issuance of Wingcoin to its customers as rewards.

Wingcoin refers to coupons and/or discount rates issued or made available to you by WingInter.

WingInter refers to WingInter Logistics Technologies Co., Ltd.

Wing Platform means marketplace service provided by WingInter which allows you to purchase any services/products made available by suppliers/merchants on WingInter’s or its partners’ platforms.

2.	GENERAL TERMS AND CONDITIONS

	i. You may earn Wingcoin from Wing Platforms and/or any other channels made available or authorized by WingInter only.

	ii. Wingcoin shall be valid for a period of 1 years from issuance date unless otherwise specify by WingInter.

	iii. WingInter reserves the right to determine your Wingcoin usage, including but not limited to the numbers and values of the Wingcoin per day and/or per transaction at its sole discretion.

	iv. Wingcoin are redeemable for any purchase/order of selected goods and/or services, determined by WingInter and made available on the Wing Platform only, subject to specific terms and conditions of the platform.

	v. Any purchase/order that exceeds the total balance of Wingcoin, such exceeded amount shall be paid by the you respectively. WingInter reserves the right to reject your order in case of insufficient balance in your account.

	vi. Wingcoin is not Wingcoinredeemable for cash, transferable or usable in conjunction with any other coupon, discount, or voucher.

	vii. In case of cancelled purchase/order transactions, Wingcoin is refundable. WingInter will refund Wingcoin directly to your balance.

	viii. In cases cancelled purchase/order transactions, WingInter shall entitled to following actions:

		a.  Revoke issued Wingcoin if you has enough Wingcoin WingInterin your balance; or

		b. Deduct net amount from your balance, in case you does not have enough Wingcoin to refundWingcoin. The deduction of net amount from your balance counterd with Wingcoint shall be calculated by WingInter’s calculation basis.

	 ix. In case of any compliant/dispute related to Wingcoin Program, you shall contact to WingInter at 078 311 311.

	x. In order to use Wingcoin, you must follow the instruction and procedures made available on Wing Platforms and/or the materials accompanying to the Wingcoin Program. Failure to do so while the order is being placed, you shall be subject to make full payment of such goods and/or services.

	xi. WingInter reserves right to revoke or cancel the Wingcoin and/or Wingcoin Program at its sole discretion. Wingcoin and Wingcoint Program shall be remained the property of WingInter.

	 xii. WingInter reserves the right to amend these terms and conditions at its sole discretion, without prior notice to you. You shall periodically review the terms and conditions to get the latest update.
